Package: dundee
Title: Deduplication of Photo Collections, Done
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("dundee", "authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: A three-phase pipeline (inventory, analyze, move) to find and
    relocate duplicate and near-duplicate photos in a large, read-only photo
    library. Inventory fingerprints every photo into a SQLite store; analyze
    clusters exact and near duplicates and serves a Shiny review app; move
    relocates preferred and non-preferred copies server-side. Built with R
    and shell only.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
