    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    DBI,
    RSQLite,
    base64enc,
    yaml
Suggests:
    shiny,
    bslib,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: libvips (vips, vipsheader, vipsthumbnail), exiftool,
    b3sum or shasum, sqlite3, ssh, a POSIX shell with find/stat/awk/sort/xargs
